- **Global Layout Structure**: Merged the previously separate [(public)](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/app/api/gateway/route.ts#25-108) and [(protected)](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/app/api/gateway/route.ts#25-108) routing layouts into a single immersive global layout in [src/app/[locale]/layout.tsx](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout.tsx). The viewport acts as a rigid, full-screen container (`100vw`/`100vh`) with the dotted CSS grid applied.
