- **Canvas Overlay**: Integrated `@react-three/fiber` as `<CanvasOverlay />` forming the foundational transparent background layer.
- **Floating Controls**: Created `<ToolsLogo />` (a fixed 48x48 Green Post-It logo in the top left) and heavily remixed the header controls into `<ToolsNavigator />` (fixed to the top right). The Navigator seamlessly toggles its inner variants depending on if a user is authenticated or visiting the public flow.
- **Legacy Cleanup**: Successfully removed legacy components and layouts (`HeaderProtected`, `LayoutProtected`, `PublicHeader`, `PublicFooter`, `partner/layout.tsx`, [(protected)/layout.tsx](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/app/api/gateway/route.ts#25-108), [(public)/layout.tsx](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/app/api/gateway/route.ts#25-108)) to fully commit to the Spatial/Canvas design paradigm.

