- **Social Login Suggestion**: Reorganized the layout within `CardAuthSocials.tsx` so that a dividing line and message appear *before* the Google and GitHub login options, correctly encouraging users to use social logins. Programmatically added the new `"socialDivider"` copy across all active languages (`it.json`, `en.json`, `es.json`, `us.json`, `fr.json`, `de.json`).

## Feature: Semantic Button Components
- **Refactored `Button.tsx`**: Completely rewrote the `buttonVariants` (cva) to include 7 discrete brand colors (`green`, `blue`, `yellow`, `fuchsia`, `violet`, `red`, `orange`) alongside explicit `light` and `dark` alternatives. Each of these supports multiple states natively (`Default`, [Muted](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/components/layout/canvas/Canvas.tsx#38-52), `Readonly`, `Outline`).
